title: Pokemon Movie 10 - The Rise of Darkrai (Standard Quality) (DivX)
description:
This is Pokemon Movie 10, entitled "The Rise of Darkrai", which was aired 2/24/08 on Cartoon Network. The movie has not yet been released on DVD, so this is a capture from the airing.

This is in DivX format and this is the Standard version of the film (It&#039;s under 700 MBs, and is of decent quality, which makes this version better for older PCs and media centers). All commercials have been removed and the movie re-spliced together to the best of my abilities using Windows Movie Maker.
